# Agent delivery workflow (IAM — always on)

Same contract as in-app Agent Sam (`agentsam_rules_document:rule_agent_delivery_workflow` + `src/core/agent-delivery-workflow.js`).

**Applies when:** active workspace is an IAM build lane (`inneranimalmedia`, `fuelnfreetime`, `companionscpas`, `inneranimalmedia-mcp`, or `SamPrimeaux/inneranimalmedia*` repo). **Does not apply** to unrelated workspaces without a ship profile.

## Order (unless user opts out)

1. Complete the work end-to-end.
2. Validate locally (build/lint/check touched files).
3. Commit + push (why-focused message; no secrets).
4. Deploy — `npm run deploy:full` from inneranimalmedia root; MCP: `cd inneranimalmedia-mcp-server && npm run deploy:full`; migrations via wrangler remote when SQL changed.
5. Follow up — shipped, verified, git ref, 1–3 next steps.

Opt-outs: `local only`, `no commit`, `no push`, `no deploy`, `plan only`, `review only`.

Do not ask permission to commit/deploy when no opt-out was given.
